column10: DESCRIPTION
The number and percent of persons in the CDM that do not have at least one record in the CONDITION_ERA table (Threshold=95%).

For the combination of CONCEPT_ID  3015377 (CALCIUM [MOLES/VOLUME] IN SERUM OR PLASMA) and UNIT_CONCEPT_ID     8753 (MILLIMOLE PER LITER), the number and percent of records that have a value less than      7.000. (Threshold=5%).

For the combination of CONCEPT_ID  3017766 (COMPLEMENT C4 [MASS/VOLUME] IN SERUM OR PLASMA) and UNIT_CONCEPT_ID     8636 (GRAM PER LITER), the number and percent of records that have a value less than      1.000. (Threshold=5%).
